{"type": "article", "id": 6430, "title": "超人鞋拔", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-17T08:53:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234122acYoPZdmxFWr9EBu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t超人与鞋子这两样看起来没什么关系的东西，被英国设计师 Duncan Shotton 组合在了一起，成为一件全新的作品超人鞋拔（Shoeperhero），此外，设计师还为其配置了一块云朵般的石头底座。两个身披斗篷的小超人各自有着截然不同的风格，红色超人身着蓝色上衣、黄色腰带以及红色徽章、裤子及靴子，黑色超人则身穿灰色上衣、黄色腰带、黑灰色徽章环以及裤子和靴子。特别的造型给了用户有趣的生活体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234121PjJUwlmpV2CkndeT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234121PY36Jm2FINyfcRVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94743276\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234121VeiNYqMbpTuUHAxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523412210FD3bgM9PJTenBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.45232274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}